🏗️ Treadstone Construction Website

📌 Project Overview
This is a responsive website for Treadstone Construction Ltd, a construction company based in Lusaka, Zambia.
The website showcases services, projects, company statistics, and provides a contact form for client enquiries.

🎯 Purpose
The goal of this website is to:
Establish an online presence for the company
Showcase construction services and past projects
Generate leads through the contact form
Improve visibility on search engines (SEO optimized)

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5 – Structure of the website
CSS3 – Styling and layout
JavaScript (Vanilla JS) – Smooth scrolling navigation
Google Fonts (Poppins) – Typography
Schema.org JSON-LD – SEO structured data

📂 Project Structure
/project-folder
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── script.js
│── /images
│     ├── background1.jpg
